body: I am quitting this server, and most likely minecraft too. I had a lot of great memories here, and I guess it is time for me to leave. I don't find this server or minecraft fun anymore, so I am leaving. I should have made this a long time ago, but was really lazy and did not want to touch this server. I will be gone for good, but you can add me on snapchat @evanhmeyer i send nudes. But anyways, I am sad to see this server just deplete in players, so I am gonna go. I remember when I rushed home from school to play this, and now I don't want to click join server.  Shoutout to Elementalassasin for being my favorite friend. Peace out girl scout
